38
00:02:30,920 --> 00:02:31,760
She's not.

39
00:02:31,760 --> 00:02:32,900
She's just a friend.

40
00:02:35,040 --> 00:02:36,280
I don't think your relationship

41
00:02:36,280 --> 00:02:37,300
is just friendship.

42
