No, it wasn't spent on her.

45
00:02:43,080 --> 00:02:44,300
Then where did the money go?

46
00:02:45,280 --> 00:02:46,120
I...

47
00:02:46,560 --> 00:02:47,800
I spent it elsewhere.

48
00:02:47,800 --> 00:02:48,860
Really, it wasn't for her.

49
00:02:49,720 --> 00:02:50,980
Not for her?

50
00:02:51,190 --> 00:02:52,040
Why are you staying

51
00:02:52,040 --> 00:02:53,420
at her family's barbecue place?

52
