and manipulative these days.

59
00:03:07,720 --> 00:03:08,600
They say

60
00:03:08,600 --> 00:03:10,400
they don't want boys to spend money

61
00:03:10,400 --> 00:03:12,680
on them to enhance their appeal.

62
00:03:12,680 --> 00:03:14,780
Sweetie, don't get tricked.

63
00:03:15,520 --> 00:03:16,960
She stays close to you

64
00:03:16,960 --> 00:03:18,440
and lets you stay at her place.

65
00:03:18,440 --> 00:03:20,220
Isn't that manipulative?

66
00:03:20,720 --> 00:03:22,440
Mom, please stop

67
00:03:22,440 --> 00:03:24,040
making baseless accusations.

68
00:03:24,040 --> 00:03:25,600
Duoduo is not like that.

69
00:03:25,600 --> 00:03:27,200
Fine, I won't say more.

70
00:03:27,200 --> 00:03:28,360
You're coming home with me.

71
00:03:28,360 --> 00:03:29,540
I'm not going.

72
