You choose.

76
00:03:36,920 --> 00:03:37,860
Mom...

77
00:03:43,430 --> 00:03:44,620
This looks great.

78
00:03:44,970 --> 00:03:45,960
Looks good.

79
00:03:45,960 --> 00:03:47,340
- This one.
- You've improved.

80
00:03:50,120 --> 00:03:50,960
Yeah.

81
00:03:55,160 --> 00:03:56,320
What's going on?

82
00:03:56,320 --> 00:03:59,520
