96
00:04:21,400 --> 00:04:22,300
Xixi,

97
00:04:23,640 --> 00:04:25,200
I apologize

98
00:04:25,200 --> 00:04:26,460
for my previous behavior,

99
00:04:27,160 --> 00:04:28,000
and I also apologize

100
00:04:28,000 --> 00:04:29,300
to all your teammates.

101
00:04:30,000 --> 00:04:31,300
I acted rashly.

102
00:04:32,120 --> 00:04:33,100
Can you forgive me?

103
00:04:36,640 --> 00:04:37,780
Are you done?

104
00:04:38,040 --> 00:04:39,120
If so, leave.

105
00:04:39,120 --> 00:04:40,540
Can't you see you're not welcome?

106
00:04:41,280 --> 00:04:42,180
Hey,

107
00:04:42,720 --> 00:04:45,100
I'm really here to apologize.

108
00:04:47,960 --> 00:04:49,900
Won't you give me a chance?

109
00:04:51,200 --> 00:04:52,600
