110
00:04:52,600 --> 00:04:53,800
Don't you want to see them?

111
00:04:53,800 --> 00:04:54,780
Please consider it.

112
00:04:59,400 --> 00:05:00,620
Let's talk privately,

113
00:05:01,480 --> 00:05:02,320
