114
00:05:03,480 --> 00:05:05,520
Why are you so persistent?

115
00:05:05,520 --> 00:05:06,360
I'll call the police.

116
00:05:06,360 --> 00:05:07,200
It's okay, Duoduo.

117
00:05:09,280 --> 00:05:10,120
Alright.

118
00:05:10,240 --> 00:05:11,460
I'll talk to you privately.

119
00:05:12,960 --> 00:05:14,760
- Xixi.
- Xixi.

120
00:05:14,760 --> 00:05:15,640
It's okay.

121
00:05:15,640 --> 00:05:17,820
What's going on between you two?

122
00:05:18,240 --> 00:05:19,560
If you don't want to go,

123
00:05:19,560 --> 00:05:20,900
