124
00:05:21,120 --> 00:05:22,460
It's fine. Don't worry.

125
00:05:23,840 --> 00:05:24,760
Let's go.

126
00:05:24,760 --> 00:05:25,820
Let's talk privately.

127
00:05:32,600 --> 00:05:34,340
Okay. Don't be mad.

128
00:05:34,640 --> 00:05:36,400
I'm here to apologize.

129
00:05:36,400 --> 00:05:37,620
I'll treat everyone to dinner.

130
00:05:39,880 --> 00:05:40,720
Please forgive me.

131
00:05:41,880 --> 00:05:42,720
No way.

132
00:05:49,080 --> 00:05:51,620
This guy really has thick skin.

133
00:05:52,180 --> 00:05:53,020
They're...

134
00:05:53,360 --> 00:05:54,650
