135
00:05:55,680 --> 00:05:57,020
That was fast.

136
00:05:57,510 --> 00:05:58,620
All good now.

137
00:06:04,160 --> 00:06:05,140
Let's go over there.

138
00:06:10,440 --> 00:06:11,700
Weilong said he wanted

139
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:14,060
