143
00:06:22,040 --> 00:06:22,980
He's treating us.

144
00:06:25,160 --> 00:06:26,000
Yeah.

145
00:06:26,200 --> 00:06:27,100
Don't get me wrong.

146
00:06:27,700 --> 00:06:29,020
We've come to know each other.

147
00:06:31,280 --> 00:06:32,120
Duoduo.

148
00:06:33,080 --> 00:06:33,920
Weilan.

149
00:06:38,720 --> 00:06:39,760
Fine.

150
00:06:39,760 --> 00:06:41,140
