181
00:07:41,560 --> 00:07:42,400
Okay.

182
00:07:42,640 --> 00:07:43,480
Mrs. Li,

183
00:07:43,880 --> 00:07:44,760
I think our promotion

184
00:07:44,760 --> 00:07:45,960
