189
00:07:53,160 --> 00:07:54,640
You're good at doing business.

190
00:07:54,640 --> 00:07:55,480
Right?

191
00:07:55,840 --> 00:07:57,240
The business has really picked up.

192
00:07:57,240 --> 00:07:58,080
Thank you.

193
00:07:58,240 --> 00:07:59,260
No problem.

194
00:08:00,600 --> 00:08:01,440
It looks

195
00:08:01,840 --> 00:08:04,260
