200
00:08:12,000 --> 00:08:13,220
Bring a plate over.

201
00:08:17,800 --> 00:08:18,640
Coming.

202
00:08:18,640 --> 00:08:19,970
- Alright, good.
- Here.

203
00:08:19,980 --> 00:08:20,960
- Eat.
- Leave it to me.

204
00:08:20,960 --> 00:08:21,800
Okay.

205
00:08:30,120 --> 00:08:31,880
Welcome, everyone!

206
00:08:31,880 --> 00:08:32,790
Eat more.

207
00:08:32,790 --> 00:08:34,000
- Enjoy!
- Coming.

208
00:08:34,000 --> 00:08:35,250
Definitely. We'll dig in.

209
00:08:35,800 --> 00:08:36,740
