212
00:08:40,720 --> 00:08:42,540
Thank you, Uncle.

213
00:08:43,510 --> 00:08:44,540
Li, just in time.

214
00:08:44,760 --> 00:08:46,640
The first drink

215
00:08:46,640 --> 00:08:48,040
