- Thanks, Coach.

220
00:08:55,320 --> 00:08:56,580
- Cheers!
- Cheers!

221
00:08:57,600 --> 00:08:58,720
Well.

222
00:08:58,720 --> 00:09:00,820
I just talked.

223
00:09:01,240 --> 00:09:03,540
The real credit goes

224
00:09:04,480 --> 00:09:06,780
to your talent and hard work.

225
00:09:07,760 --> 00:09:09,220
This drink is for you.

226
00:09:09,680 --> 00:09:11,200
- Thank you, Dafu.
- Thank you.

227
00:09:11,200 --> 00:09:13,460
- Thanks, Coach.
- Thanks, Uncle.

228
00:09:21,160 --> 00:09:22,580
That's enough, Dad.

229
00:09:23,070 --> 00:09:23,920
Good drinkers!

230
00:09:23,920 --> 00:09:25,640
- Duoduo, get everything ready.
- Okay.

231
00:09:25,640 --> 00:09:26,480
- You go.
- Enjoy.

232
00:09:26,480 --> 00:09:27,460
I'll handle it.

233
00:09:27,720 --> 00:09:29,110
Eat up while it's hot.

234
00:09:29,120 --> 00:09:30,320
Come on, eat, eat!

235
00:09:30,320 --> 00:09:31,760
- Try this.
- This.

236
00:09:31,760 --> 00:09:32,820
- This is good.
- Coach.

237
00:09:32,820 --> 00:09:33,660
Sure.

238
00:09:33,840 --> 00:09:34,820
Coach, you eat too.

239
00:09:35,800 --> 00:09:38,000
You two are so sweet.

240
00:09:38,000 --> 00:09:39,080
Please stop.

241
00:09:39,080 --> 00:09:39,980
