246
00:09:45,920 --> 00:09:47,760
Let's bow to the power.

247
00:09:47,760 --> 00:09:49,540
How about we punish ourselves with a drink?

248
00:09:49,960 --> 00:09:50,820
Go on.

249
00:09:51,840 --> 00:09:52,940
Fill it up.

250
00:09:53,200 --> 00:09:54,380
We'll drink on our own.

251
00:09:55,020 --> 00:09:56,220
- Not with us.
- Cheers!

252
00:09:56,440 --> 00:09:57,720
- Just us then.
- Coach!

253
00:09:57,720 --> 00:09:58,660
We'll drink.

254
00:09:59,160 --> 00:10:00,580
- Coach, come on.
- Sure.

255
00:10:05,400 --> 00:10:07,000
- Well.
- Eat up.

256
00:10:07,000 --> 00:10:08,300
I was wrong last time.

257
00:10:08,600 --> 00:10:11,180
I'm apologizing again today.

258
00:10:12,920 --> 00:10:14,100
Can I refuse?

259
00:10:16,360 --> 00:10:17,520
Of course.

260
00:10:17,520 --> 00:10:18,590
It's your choice.

261
00:10:19,880 --> 00:10:20,780
Well said.

262
00:10:21,040 --> 00:10:22,760
Apologizing is your choice.

263
00:10:22,760 --> 00:10:24,300
Forgiving is mine.

264
00:10:25,000 --> 00:10:26,700
