273
00:10:48,240 --> 00:10:49,080
What do I want?

274
00:10:49,240 --> 00:10:50,140
It's simple.

275
00:10:50,560 --> 00:10:51,520
Open a shop,

276
00:10:51,520 --> 00:10:52,520
