285
00:11:12,800 --> 00:11:14,520
Yes, to Xiaojing and Xixi!

286
00:11:14,520 --> 00:11:15,680
You can do it!

287
00:11:15,680 --> 00:11:17,360
- Go for it!
- Thanks, everyone.

288
00:11:17,360 --> 00:11:18,440
You can do it.

289
00:11:18,440 --> 00:11:20,040
- Cheers.
